ygData.messageBody:
Hey whats up? I dont really post much to this list, but i dont know about
you guys but i enjoy reading stories about other peoples experiences in the
game, especially higher levels cause i havent even come close yet, my highest
is a level 19 warrior and i ahve a level 9 (will be 10 in an hour i hope)
Cleric. Would be cool if people would tell about there experiences in the
game.

Falorrn
Level 9 Cleric of Mithaniel Marr
